quran[88]{c,v,t}:
  38,1,Swad! Ndahiye iyi Qur’an yuje urwibutso
  38,2,Nyamara abahakanye bari mu bwibone n’ubwigomeke
  38,3,"Ese ni ibisekuru bingahe tworetse mbere yabo, bigatakamba by’impitagihe"
  38,4,(Abarabu b’ababangikanyamana) batangajwe no kugerwaho n’umuburizi (Muhamadi) ubakomokamo. Nuko abahakanyi baravuga bati “Uyu ni umurozi w’umubeshyi.”
  38,5,"“(Arafata) imana (zacu) zose akazigira Imana imwe? Mu by’ukuri, iki ni ikintu gitangaje!”"
  38,6,Maze ibikomerezwa muri bo bigenda bivuga biti “Nimugende mutsimbarare ku mana zanyu. Mu by’ukuri iki ni ikintu gikenewe.”
  38,7,Ibi ntitwigeze tubyumva mu myizerere yo hambere. Ibi nta kindi biri cyo usibye kuba ari ibihimbano
  38,8,"Ese ni we wenyine muri twe waba waramanuriwe urwibutso? Ahubwo barashidikanya ku rwibutso rwanjye (Qur’an), kuko batarumva ku bihano byanjye"
  38,9,"Ese baba bafite ibigega by’impuhwe za Nyagasani wawe, Umunyacyubahiro bihebuje, Ugaba bihebuje"
  38,10,"Cyangwa baba bafite ubwami bw’ibirere n’isi ndetse n’ibiri hagati yabyo? Niba ari uko bimeze, ngaho nibazamuke mu kirere bakoresheje uburyo ubwo ari bwo bwose (maze bakumire ubutumwa)"
  38,11,Zimwe mu ngabo z’udutsiko zizakubitirwa inshuro aha ngaha (nk’uko iz’udutsiko ari ko byazigendekeye mbere)
  38,12,"Mbere yabo, abantu ba Nuhu, aba Adi ndetse na Farawo wari ufite inyubako zisongoye (piramide) barahinyuye"
  38,13,"N’aba Thamudu, abantu ba Lutwi ndetse n’aba Ayikat (b’i Madiyani), bose bari udutsiko"
  38,14,"Nta na kamwe muri two katahinyuye intumwa, nuko ibihano byanjye biba impamo"
  38,15,Aba nta kindi bategereje kitari urusaku rumwe rudasubira
  38,16,Kandi baravuze bati “Nyagasani wacu! Twihutishirize umugabane wacu (ibihano) mbere y’uko umunsi w’ibarura ugera.”
  38,17,"Ihanganire ibyo bavuga (yewe Muhamadi), kandi wibuke umugaragu wacu Dawudi wari umunyembaraga (mu guhangana n’umwanzi). Mu by’ukuri yicuzaga kuri Allah cyane"
  38,18,Mu by’ukuri twashoboje imisozi gufatanya na we (Dawudi) kudusingiza buri uko bwije n’uko bucyeye
  38,19,"Ndetse n’inyoni zikusanyirijwe hamwe, zaramwumviye (zifatanya na we mu kudusingiza)"
  38,20,"Maze dukomeza ubwami bwe, tunamuha ubushishozi no guca imanza neza"
  38,21,"Ese (yewe Muhamadi) inkuru y’abari bashyamiranye yaba yarakugezeho, ubwo buriraga bagasanga (Dawudi) aho yasengeraga (Mih’rab)"
  38,22,"Ubwo binjiraga kwa Dawudi maze akabikanga, bakavuga bati “Wigira ubwoba! Twembi twashyamiranye; umwe muri twe yahuguje undi. Bityo dukiranure mu kuri kandi ntubogame, ndetse unatuyobore inzira igororotse.”"
  38,23,"Mu by’ukuri uyu muvandimwe wanjye afite intama mirongo cyenda n’icyenda, mu gihe njye mfite intama imwe (gusa), ariko yavuze ati “Na yo yindagize!” (Nyamara njye simbishaka), none yandushije ijwi"
  38,24,"(Dawudi atabanje kumva undi) aravuga ati “Rwose yaguhuguje kuba yagusabye intama yawe ngo ayongere mu ze. Kandi mu by’ukuri abenshi mu bafatanyije imitungo barahuguzanya, uretse ba bandi bemeye bakanakora ibikorwa byiza; kandi ni bo bake.” Nuko Dawudi amenya ko twamugerageje asaba imbabazi Nyagasani we, yitura hasi yubamye, anicuza (kuri Allah)"
  38,25,Nuko ibyo turabimubabarira. Kandi mu by’ukuri ari hafi yacu ndetse azagira igarukiro ryiza (Ijuru)
  38,26,"Yewe Dawudi! Mu by’ukuri twakugize umusigire ku isi, bityo jya ukiranura abantu mu kuri kandi ntuzagendere ku marangamutima, kugira ngo atazavaho akuyobya inzira ya Allah. Mu by’ukuri abazayoba inzira ya Allah bazahanishwa ibihano bikaze, kubera kwibagirwa umunsi w’ibarura"
  38,27,"Ntitwanaremye ikirere n’isi ndetse n’ibiri hagati yabyo nta mpamvu. Uko ni ko abahakanye bibwira. Bityo, ibihano bikaze by’umuriro bizaba ku bahakanyi"
  38,28,Ese abemeye bakanakora ibikorwa byiza twabafata kimwe n’abangizi ku isi? Cyangwa se twafata kimwe abagandukira Allah n’inkozi z’ibibi
  38,29,"Iki ni igitabo cyuje imigisha twaguhishuriye (yewe Muhamadi), kugira ngo (abantu) batekereze ku mirongo yacyo ndetse no kugira ngo abanyabwenge bibuke"
  38,30,Kandi Dawudi twamuhaye Sulayimani nk’impano. Yari umugaragu mwiza. Mu by’ukuri yicuzaga kuri Allah cyane
  38,31,(Ibuka) ubwo nimugoroba yamurikirwaga amafarasi y’ubwoko bwiza kandi yiruka cyane
  38,32,"Nuko akavuga ati “Nakunze imitungo y’isi kugeza ubwo nibagirwa Nyagasani wanjye, izuba ririnda rirenga!”"
  38,33,“Ngaho nimuzingarurire!” Maze atangira kuzagaza ku maguru no ku majosi
  38,34,"Kandi rwose twagerageje Sulayimani tujugunya ikibiri ku ntebe ye y’ubwami, (bimutera gusa nk’utakaje ubwami bwe, abona ko yageragejwe) nyuma yicuza ku Mana"
  38,35,"Aravuga ati “Nyagasani wanjye! Mbabarira, unangabire ubwami butazigera buhabwa n’umwe nyuma yanjye. Mu by’ukuri ni wowe ugaba bihebuje.”"
  38,36,"Nuko dutegeka umuyaga kumwumvira, ugahuha ku itegeko rye buke buke (akawerekeza) aho ashaka (kujya hose)"
  38,37,Ndetse n’amajini y’amoko yose; ayubaka n’ayibira mu mazi (twayategetse kumwumvira)
  38,38,Naho andi (yamwigomekagaho yayahambiraga) ku minyururu
  38,39,"(Allah abwira Sulayimani ati) “Ibi ni impano yacu; bityo ha (uwo ushatse) cyangwa wime (uwo ushatse), nta cyo uzabazwa"
  38,40,Kandi mu by’ukuri yari hafi yacu ndetse azagira igarukiro ryiza (Ijuru)
  38,41,Unibuke ubwo umugaragu wacu Ayubu yatakambiraga Nyagasani we agira ati “Mu by’ukuri Shitani yanteje ibyago n’ububabare.”
  38,42,(Allah aramubwira ati) “Kubita ikirenge cyawe hasi; ayo mazi akonje (avuyemo) ni ayo kwiyuhagira no kunywa.”
  38,43,"Nuko ku bw’impuhwe ziduturutseho, tumugarurira umuryango we uri kumwe n’abandi nka wo, kugira ngo bibe urwibutso ku banyabwenge"
  38,44,"Unafate umuba w’udushari mu kuboko kwawe maze uwukubitishe (umugore wawe), kugira ngo udatatira indahiro. Mu by’ukuri twasanze (Ayubu) ari umuntu wihangana. Mbega ukuntu yari umugaragu mwiza! Kandi rwose yicuzaga kenshi (kuri Allah)"
  38,45,"Kandi wibuke (yewe Muhamadi) abagaragu bacu; Ibrahimu, Isihaka na Yakubu; bari abanyamurava (mu kutugaragira) bakanagira ubushishozi (mu idini)"
  38,46,Mu by’ukuri twarabatoranyije tubaha umwihariko wo kwibuka imperuka
  38,47,"Kandi rwose imbere yacu bari mu ntoranywa, mu beza kurusha abandi"
  38,48,"Unibuke Isimayili, Aliyasa na Dhul’kifli; bose bari mu beza kurusha abandi"
  38,49,Iyi (Qur’an) ni urwibutso. Kandi mu by’ukuri abagandukira (Allah) bazagira igarukiro ryiza
  38,50,"Ijuru rihoraho, bazafungurirwa imiryango yaryo"
  38,51,"Aho bazaba begamye, batumiza imbuto nyinshi n’ibinyobwa"
  38,52,Bazaba bari kumwe n’abagore barangamiye abagabo babo (gusa) kandi b’urungano
  38,53,Ibyo ni byo (bihembo) mwasezeranyijwe ku munsi w’ibarura
  38,54,Mu by’ukuri ibyo ni amafunguro yacu adateze kuzashira
  38,55,Ibyo (ni byo bizagororerwa abemeramana). Naho abanyabyaha bazagira igarukiro ribi
  38,56,Jahanamu bazahiramo. Mbega ubuturo bubi
  38,57,"Ibyo (ni byo bihano bazahanishwa). Bityo, nibabyumve; ni amazi yatuye n’amashyira"
  38,58,N’ibindi (bihano) bimeze nka byo by’ingeri nyinshi
  38,59,"(Abayobeje abandi bazabwirwa bati) “Aka ni agatsiko kiroshye mu gihe kimwe namwe (mu muriro)”, (bavuge bati) “Nta heza bashyikiye kuko mu by’ukuri, bagiye guhira mu muriro.”"
  38,60,(Abayobejwe) bazavuga bati “Ahubwo ni mwe mutashyikiye aheza kuko ari mwe mwawudukururiye (umuriro); kandi ni cyo cyicaro kibi.”
  38,61,Bazavuga bati “Nyagasani wacu! Uwadukururiye ibi mwongerere ibihano byo mu muriro byikubye kabiri.”
  38,62,Bazanavuga bati “Byatugendekeye bite ko tutabona bamwe mu bantu twabaraga mu nkozi z’ibibi?”
  38,63,"Ese twabibeshyagaho (ku isi) tubannyega (naho ari abantu b’intungane, cyangwa bari kumwe natwe mu muriro) amaso yacu akaba atababona"
  38,64,"Mu by’ukuri, uko ni ko gusubiranamo kw’abantu bo mu muriro"
  38,65,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti “Njye nta kindi ndi cyo usibye kuba ndi umuburizi, kandi nta yindi mana ikwiye gusengwa by’ukuri itari Allah; Umwe rukumbi, Umunyembaraga w’ikirenga"
  38,66,"Nyagasani w’ibirere n’isi ndetse n’ibiri hagati yabyo, Umunyacyubahiro bihebuje,Umunyembabazi uhebuje.”"
  38,67,Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti “Iyi (Qur’an) ni inkuru ihambaye
  38,68,Ariko mwayiteye umugongo
  38,69,Nta bumenyi nari mfite ku bamalayika bo mu ijuru ubwo bajyaga impaka (ku iremwa rya Adamu)
  38,70,Usibye ko nabihishuriwe kuko ndi umuburizi ugaragara.”
  38,71,(Ibuka) ubwo Nyagasani wawe yabwiraga abamalayika ati “Mu by’ukuri ngiye kurema umuntu mu ibumba.”
  38,72,"Nimara kumutunganya nkanamuhuhamo roho inturutseho, mumwikubite imbere mwubamye"
  38,73,Nuko abamalayika bose barubama
  38,74,Usibye Ibilisi (Shitani) wagize ubwibone maze akaba mu bahakanye
  38,75,(Nuko Allah akavuga ati) “Yewe Ibilisi! Ni iki cyakubujije kubamira uwo naremye n’amaboko yanjye yombi? Ese wagize ubwibone cyangwa wiyumva nk’uri mu bo mu nzego zo hejuru?”
  38,76,"(Ibilisi) iravuga iti “Njye ndi mwiza kumurusha kuko wandemye mu muriro, we ukamurema mu ibumba.”"
  38,77,"(Allah) aravuga ati “Ngaho sohoka aha ( mu ijuru), kuko ubaye ikivume.”"
  38,78,Kandi rwose umuvumo wanjye uzagukurikirana kuzageza ku munsi w’ibihembo
  38,79,(Ibilisi) iravuga iti “Nyagasani wanjye! Mpa kuramba kuzageza ku munsi (abapfuye) bazazurirwaho.”
  38,80,(Allah) aravuga ati “Mu by’ukuri ubaye mu bazaramba
  38,81,Kugeza ku munsi w’igihe kizwi.”
  38,82,"(Ibilisi) iravuga iti “Ndahiye ku bw’icyubahiro cyawe, ko rwose nzabayobya bose"
  38,83,“Uretse abagaragu bawe b’indobanure muri bo.”
  38,84,"(Allah) avuga arahira ati “Ni ukuri, kandi ibyo mvuga ni ukuri"
  38,85,Ko wowe na bamwe mu bazagukurikira nzabuzurisha umuriro wa Jahanamu.”
  38,86,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti “Ntabwo (kubagezaho ubutumwa) mbibasabira igihembo na kimwe, ndetse nta n’ubwo ndi mu bishushanya (bigira intumwa batari zo, banakora ibyo batategetswe).”"
  38,87,“Iyi (Qur’an) nta kindi iri cyo usibye kuba ari urwibutso ku biremwa byose.”
  38,88,“Kandi rwose muzamenya inkuru yayo bidatinze”